    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or dependable beater with a strong-running powertrain, responsive throttle, and a driveline that feels honest and usable. Not a show car, but it has the kind of mechanical simplicity and serviceable underpinnings that make it appealing for someone who wants an affordable daily, shop car, or weekend fixer. Starts, runs, and moves out well, with good bones for the next owner to sort cosmetics and odds and ends. Priced right for a practical buyer who values function over flash.",
